<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,414,258,283]" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">Regional distribution.</emphasis>
SeVeral localitieS of thiS SpecieS 
<collectingCounty box="[795,1012,258,283]" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">Situated in WeStern</collectingCounty>
and Central 
<collectingCountry box="[1161,1270,258,283]" name="Mongolia" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">Mongolia</collectingCountry>
were reVealed during thiS Study. The moSt recent findingS were made in the 
<collectingRegion box="[876,952,294,319]" country="Mongolia" name="Hovd" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">KhoVd</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingMunicipality box="[1014,1175,294,319]" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">ZaVkhan riVer</collectingMunicipality>
baSinS, where 
<taxonomicName authority="O.F.Müller, 1773" authorityName="Middendorff" authorityYear="1851" class="Gastropoda" family="Valvatidae" genus="Valvata" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ectobranchia" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="sibirica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="53">Valvata sibirica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
inhabitS Small floodplain lakeS and Shallow zoneS of large lakeS (Khoit Dalai Nuur, Ugiy Nuur) rich with aquatic Vegetation. It waS alSo recorded from Northern Mongolia—HöVSgöl lake and 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D787F9356BFFE51CF1EEE91149E1F6:8EA16034356BFFE51800EF1F163BE3B7" box="[1126,1282,366,391]" country="Mongolia" county="Situated in WeStern" municipality="ZaVkhan riVer" name="Orkhon RiVer" pageId="8" pageNumber="53" stateProvince="KhoVd">Orkhon RiVer</location>
